text: Nathan Alejandro Arenas (born September 30, 2005) is an American child actor. He auditioned for his very first role ever, like co-star Nina Lu, in the Disney Channel series BUNK'D (a spinoff of Jessie) as Jorge. He also played Robbie in the ABC Studios TV series Criminal Minds and Danny in the Disney+ series Diary of a Future President. Arenas is of Mexican descent.
